Leeson Feed-auger drive motor,
Dust-tight, capacitator start motor with your choice of field proven electronc or protected mechanical starting switch--both eliminate damage caused when motor is over-speeded by obstructed auger. Ball-bearing, heavy duty industrial quality designs for high overload capacity. Side mounted conduit box. Flange mounts directly to drive assembly. Fully gasketed to keep out feed dust. Has screw driver slot in rear shaft. Continuous duty, with manual thermal overload protection.
Features:
  • Steel frame
  • Dust tight
  • Shaft is 5/8” Dia. X 1. 97” ling with 3/16” keyway
  • Choice of mechanical or solid state starting switch
  • Capacitor start/capcitor run design for reduced amperage
  • Mechanical switch has over-speed protection
  • Manual overload protected
  • Footnotes: S, MX, 27, 51, 53
Note

Motors of 3/4 HP and less in the two adjacent charts have shaft of 1/2" diameter x 1 1/2" length, with flat; motors 1 HP and larger have 5/8" diameter x 1. 97" length, with key.

Rugged three phase jet pump motor for industrial service.
  • Steel frame
  • C-Face no base
  • Dripproof
  • 5/8" shaft output diameter
  • NEMA 56 C face mounting flange
  • Threaded shafts made of 303 grade stainless steel
  • CCW rotation facing lead end
  • Quiet flow-through ventilation system
  • Double sealed bearings on shaft end
  • Terminal board with quick connects
  • Locked shaft end bearings
  • UL recognized and CSA certified
  • Footnotes: S, MX

Same design Features as Leeson's standard Premium Stainless and Extreme Duck motors with built-in Shaft Grounding Rings designed to protect motors used in Applications such as AC inverters to control the speed of the motors. They eliminate the stray voltages that may damage the motor’s bearings.

Dust-tight, capacitator start motor with your choice of field proven electronc or protected mechanical starting switch--both eliminate damage caused when motor is over-speeded by obstructed auger. Ball-bearing, heavy duty industrial quality designs for high overload capacity. Side mounted conduit box. Flange mounts directly to drive assembly. Fully gasketed to keep out feed dust. Has screw driver slot in rear shaft. Continuous duty, with manual thermal overload protection.

  • Manual overload protected
